function Teaching(): JSX.Element { return (

TEACHING

Data Science: Data Driven Decision Making, Teaching Assistant, Copenhagen Business School, fall semester 2020.

Mathematical Optimization: Models, Methods and Applications, Teaching Assistant, Copenhagen Business School, fall semester 2020.

Data Science: Data Driven Decision Making, Teaching Assistant, Copenhagen Business School, fall semester 2021.

Predictive Analytics, Teaching Assistant, Copenhagen Business School, spring semester 2023.

DISSEMINATIO

Machine Learning NeEDS Mathematical Optimization online seminar series, Co-organizer, January 2021 – March 2022.

32nd European Conference on Operational Research, Espoo (Finland), Co-organizer of the stream “Machine Learning and Mathematical Optimization”, July 2022.

Early Stage Researcher Representative of the Steering Board of the H2020 Marie Skłodowska-Curie Program Research and Innovation Staff Exchange Network of European Data Scientists project (NeEDS), Ref. 822214, 1 October 2022-to present.
